title: Ep 2599 - Popatlals Misery
shortDesc: It's Bhai Dooj and Popatlal wants to celebrate this festival of brothers and sisters with his sisters in the Gokuldham society but when he goes to each of their houses to wish them and give them gifts

title: Ep 2600 - A Surprise for Popatlal
shortDesc: The ladies of Gokuldham society surprise Popatlal on the occasion of Bhai Dooj. Popatlal is overwhelmed seeing that he is loved by his sisters. Meanwhile, Jethalal again finds himself in fresh trouble.

title: Ep 2601 - Happy Childrens Day
shortDesc: Jethalal loses the keys to Gada electronics and Champaklal gets mad at him so they both try to find the keys in their house. Later Jethalal, Bhide, Mehta, Iyer & Babita, and Dr. Hathi meet in the compound of the society

title: Ep 2602 - Bhides Worry
shortDesc: Bhide notices that Sameer, one of his students, hasn't been doing well in the exams. Bhide gets worried about Sameer's future and shares his worries with Madhvi.

title: Ep 2603 - The Ideal Teacher
shortDesc: Bhide, who is worried about Sameer's future, decides to return the tuition fees to Sameer's parents. Going against Madhvi's advice, Bhide meets Sameer's parents and informs them about his inability to improve Sameer's marks.

title: Ep 2604 - A Teachers Advice
shortDesc: Bhide was worried about one of his student Sameer's marks dropping in the exams so he decides to ask Tapu and friends for advice. Bhide gives Sameer's parents the perfect solution which helps Sameer to improve his marks.

title: Ep 2605 - Risky Business
shortDesc: Taarak Mehta calls up Jethalal and learns that Jethalal is getting tired of running a business. Jethalal feels he should have found a 9 to 5 job as running a business is risky.

title: Ep 2606 - Work Frustrations
shortDesc: Jethalal returns from work frustrated to the boiling point and all the men of Gokuldham society gather at Abdul's shop for their soda session and discuss their work frustrations.

title: Ep 2607 - Selling The Business
shortDesc: After their stressful soda session at Abdul's shop, Taarak is worried about Jethalal as he discusses it with Anjali. The next day Bhide finds out in a newspaper advertisement that Jethalal has put Gada electronics for sale

title: Ep 2608 - Trouble For Jethalal
shortDesc: Jethalal finds himself in yet another trouble. Tarak Mehta calls up Jethalal and asks him to meet him urgently. Before Taarak Mehta can reveal anything, Champaklal vents out his anger on Jethalal.

title: Ep 2609 - Jethalals Misery
shortDesc: Jethalal assures Champaklal that he hasn't given the ad in the newspaper. When Jethalal reaches Gada Electronics, he finds Nattu Kaka and Baga celebrating. Nattu and Baga inform Jethalal that they gave the ad in the newspaper.

title: Ep 2610 - The Flashbacks
shortDesc: A worried Champaklal arrives at Gada Electronics. Then, Nattu Kaka and Baga help Jethalal remember the moments when he had urged them to sell Gada Electronics.

title: Ep 2611 - Nattu and Baghas Explanation
shortDesc: Jethalal and Champaklal furious after seeing the advertisement about Gada Electronics being on sale, reach the showroom to eventually find out that it was Nattu Kaka and Bagha who put up the advertisement.

title: Ep 2612 - Bad Decisions
shortDesc: Two men come to Gada Electronics and ask Jethalal to leave the showroom space in a given time as someone else has bought the space after coming across the advertisement in the newspaper.

title: Ep 2613 - Enters Surma Bhai
shortDesc: Two men warn Jethalal to leave the place as someone else has bought it after coming across the advertisement in the newspaper and the person who has bought the place is none other than an infamous gangster Surma Bhai.
